node.text:
The Ultimate Surfer Sweepstakes gives you the chance to win a once-in-a-lifetime surf session at Surf Ranch. You and three friends can ride 700-yard perfect waves all to yourselves, stay in the Surf Ranch Airstreams, and win new Outerknown gear. Enter, link in bio. @ultimatesurferabc 

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S./D.C., age 18+ (19+ in AL and NE, 21+ in MS). Void outside 50 U.S./D.C. and where prohibited. Ends 09/22/21 For full Official Rules, visit TheUltimateSurferSweeps.com.
